Output demo.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 860
Set Height 520
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Sleep 500ms

Type "cd /tmp/demo-nextjs && ls package.json"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "cat package.json | head -5"
Enter
Sleep 1.5s

Type@0ms ""
Sleep 500ms

Type "onerules"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 3s
